  "translations": {
    "en": "al-Harith b. al-Mughira al-Nasri from Abi `Abdillah al-Sadiq (as). He said: Whoever hears the mu’adhin say “I bear witness that there is no god but Allah, and I bear witness that Muhammad is the Messenger of Allah” and says, in confirmation and expectation, “And I bear witness that there is no god but Allah and that Muhammad is the Messenger of Allah”, it will be sufficient for him against all who reject and deny, and it will assist anyone who believes and testifies to it. He will receive a reward for every person who rejects, denies, believes, and testifies.",
    "ur": "al-Harith b. al-Mughira al-Nasri from Abi `Abdillah al-Sadiq (as). He said: Whoever hears the mu’adhin say “I bear witness that there is no god but Allah, and I bear witness that Muhammad is the Messenger of Allah” and says, in confirmation and expectation, “And I bear witness that there is no god but Allah and that Muhammad is the Messenger of Allah”, it will be sufficient for him against all who reject and deny, and it will assist anyone who believes and testifies to it. He will receive a reward for every person who rejects, denies, believes, and testifies.",
    "tr": "al-Harith b. al-Mughira al-Nasri from Abi `Abdillah al-Sadiq (as). He said: Whoever hears mu’adhin say “I bear witness that there is no god but Allah, and I bear witness that Muhammad is Messenger of Allah” and says, in confirmation and expectation, “And I bear witness that there is no god but Allah and that Muhammad is Messenger of Allah”, it will be sufficient for him against all who reject and deny, and it will assist anyone who believes and testifies to it. He will receive a reward for every person who rejects, denies, believes, and testifies. [Türkçe çeviri]",
    "fa": "al-Harith b. al-Mughira al-Nasri from Abi `Abdillah al-Sadiq (as). He said: Whoever hears the mu’adhin say “I bear witness that there is no god but Allah, and I bear witness that Muhammad is the Messenger of Allah” and says, in confirmation and expectation, “And I bear witness that there is no god but Allah and that Muhammad is the Messenger of Allah”, it will be sufficient for him against all who reject and deny, and it will assist anyone who believes and testifies to it. He will receive a reward for every person who rejects, denies, believes, and testifies.",
    "id": "al-Harith b. al-Mughira al-Nasri from Abi `Abdillah al-Sadiq (as). He said: Whoever hears the mu’adhin say “I bear witness that there is no god but Allah, and I bear witness that Muhammad is the Messenger of Allah” and says, in confirmation and expectation, “And I bear witness that there is no god but Allah and that Muhammad is the Messenger of Allah”, it will be sufficient for him against all who reject and deny, and it will assist anyone who believes and testifies to it. He will receive a reward for every person who rejects, denies, believes, and testifies.",
    "bn": "al-Harith b. al-Mughira al-Nasri from Abi `Abdillah al-Sadiq (as). He said: Whoever hears the mu’adhin say “I bear witness that there is no god but Allah, and I bear witness that Muhammad is the Messenger of Allah” and says, in confirmation and expectation, “And I bear witness that there is no god but Allah and that Muhammad is the Messenger of Allah”, it will be sufficient for him against all who reject and deny, and it will assist anyone who believes and testifies to it. He will receive a reward for every person who rejects, denies, believes, and testifies.",
    "es": "al-Harith b. al-Mughira al-Nasri from Abi `Abdillah al-Sadiq (as). He said: Whoever hears el mu’adhin say “I bear witness that there is no god but Allah, and I bear witness that Muhammad is el Messenger of Allah” and says, in confirmation and expectation, “And I bear witness that there is no god but Allah and that Muhammad is el Messenger of Allah”, it will be sufficient for him against all who reject and deny, and it will assist anyone who believes and testifies to it. He will receive a reward for every person who rejects, denies, believes, and testifies. [Traducción]",
    "fr": "al-Harith b. al-Mughira al-Nasri from Abi `Abdillah al-Sadiq (as). He said: Whoever hears le mu’adhin say “I bear witness that there is no god but Allah, and I bear witness that Muhammad is le Messenger of Allah” and says, in confirmation and expectation, “And I bear witness that there is no god but Allah and that Muhammad is le Messenger of Allah”, it will be sufficient for him against all who reject and deny, and it will assist anyone who believes and testifies to it. He will receive a reward for every person who rejects, denies, believes, and testifies. [Traduction française]",
    "de": "al-Harith b. al-Mughira al-Nasri from Abi `Abdillah al-Sadiq (as). He said: Whoever hears mu’adhin say “I bear witness that there is no god but Allah, and I bear witness that Muhammad is Messenger of Allah” and says, in confirmation and expectation, “And I bear witness that there is no god but Allah and that Muhammad is Messenger of Allah”, it will be sufficient for him against all who reject and deny, and it will assist anyone who believes and testifies to it. He will receive a reward for every person who rejects, denies, believes, and testifies. [Übersetzung]",
    "ru": "al-Harith b. al-Mughira al-Nasri from Abi `Abdillah al-Sadiq (as). He said: Whoever hears the mu’adhin say “I bear witness that there is no god but Allah, and I bear witness that Muhammad is the Messenger of Allah” and says, in confirmation and expectation, “And I bear witness that there is no god but Allah and that Muhammad is the Messenger of Allah”, it will be sufficient for him against all who reject and deny, and it will assist anyone who believes and testifies to it. He will receive a reward for every person who rejects, denies, believes, and testifies.",
    "zh": "al-Harith b. al-Mughira al-Nasri from Abi `Abdillah al-Sadiq (as). He said: Whoever hears the mu’adhin say “I bear witness that there is no god but Allah, and I bear witness that Muhammad is the Messenger of Allah” and says, in confirmation and expectation, “And I bear witness that there is no god but Allah and that Muhammad is the Messenger of Allah”, it will be sufficient for him against all who reject and deny, and it will assist anyone who believes and testifies to it. He will receive a reward for every person who rejects, denies, believes, and testifies."
